{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, at that time, most of the-- now, I have to tell you, there is such a thing as a kapo, which was a Camp Polizei and there is a jupo, which one is Juden Polizei.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, in Mauthausen, in the camp, there was a man who was in charge, a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was killed, I think, after when we were liberated, by the other Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had about four very well-fed companions who was keeping him from getting into trouble, like, that the rest of the Jews are not going to kill him because he was a very, very rude man.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was just as rude as it would have been an SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a kapo, I guess, it's a Camp Polizei, Juden Polizei, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we have-- that's a place where I have met my cousin, and my cousin was so-- he was about 42 years old and he was in such bad shape that he was asking me if I have any toothpaste.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, what toothpaste?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, well, I'm eating toothpaste, he said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was willing to eat anything which had some substance, which one was resembling food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he died about two or three days after.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was in very, very bad shape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How long were you at Mauthausen?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I wasn't there too long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it must have been about 10 days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just trying to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was water at one point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At this time, the water was running water because Mauthausen was built very properly by the Germans where there was water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there isn't much else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We, as I told you, we were carrying food or soup or black something.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
